name: Pardofelis | Honkai Impact 3rd | LoRA
description:
A LoRA Model of Pardofelis from Honkai Impact 3rd🐈🐈

This LoRA includes three official costumes.

There are three sets of trigger words:

For trigger Reverist Calico(Default Skin):😸

pardofelis (reverist calico) (honkai impact), pardofelis (honkai impact), heterochromia, official costume, cat girl, blue eyes, green eyes, light brown hair, mole under eye, black bikini, black skirt, frilled skirt, bikini top only

If you prefer Pardo🐈 wearing a hood, you may append hood, white hood, hood up

For trigger Midsummer Collector(Summer Outfit):😽

pardofelis (midsummer collector) (honkai impact), pardofelis (honkai impact), heterochromia, frilled bikini, swimsuit, pink bow, official alternate costume, cat girl, bright pupils, blue eyes, green eyes, light brown hair, mole under eye

experimental:For trigger Spectral Claws(Pink Jacket):😼

bonus: For trigger Any Custom Outfit:😺

pardofelis (honkai impact), (heterochromia:1.1), alternate costume, cat girl, bright pupils, blue eyes, green eyes, light brown hair, mole under eye, light brown hair, cat girl, [your idea......]

Recommend 0.9-1 Strength for triggering any official costume.

For changing custom clothes, I suggest 0.75-0.9 Weight

The preview images were generated by AbyssOrangeMix2 Model.

In some instances applied ControlNet.

I am using the NAI model [e6e8e1fc] to train, including [f458b5c6] VAE.

Able to work with all mixed models based on NAI(i.e. AbyssOrangeMix, Anything v3)

If you like this LORA, please comment and give it a like.❤️

Any suggestions are welcome to comment here.

And also welcome to share your creations.

Enjoy it!
